      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GAMBELLA (6) is worth forgiving for her last effort when seventh (35.32) at this track over 600m. Form here at the trip excellent including five wins. Solid formlines coming through her last run. Has winning claims on her best figures. PAW DAMON (2) impressive display when ran right away after leading to make it back to back wins, scoring at Sandown over 515m (29.43). Leading player again. GENERAL FRANKY (3) is a consistent dog overall, in the frame at seven of 18 starts including seven wins but missed the frame latest when fifth (30.20) over 520m at Geelong. Boasts an unbeaten record from this box. Super consistent and can feature with the right run. GO GO EVIE (1) was unplaced here last start but gets her chance to atone.",
